import React from 'react'
import { Grid } from "@mui/material"

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <MainNavbar>
            <Container>
                <Grid container spacing={3}>
                    <Grid></Grid>
                    <Grid></Grid>
                    <Grid></Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Container>
        </MainNavbar>
    )
}

export default Navbar
